<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> To facilitate efficient official monitoring of dietary foods for specialmedical purposes, when a product is placed on the market, the manufacturer, orwhere a product is manufactured in a third country, the importer, shall notifythe competent authority of the Member States where the product is beingmarketed by forwarding to it a model of the label used for the product. </inglise>
